40:52.488 --> 40:55.672
No matter what he's done, no matter what he's done, never run for God.

40:56.233 --> 41:00.178
Runs to the Savior, runs to God and owns it.

41:00.354 --> 41:02.497
and says, Lord, I am so sorry.

41:02.717 --> 41:06.062
He didn't have to come to his people and say, look, I'm sorry.

41:06.082 --> 41:09.547
He goes to God on his knees and says, oh, God, I've sinned against you.

41:10.489 --> 41:10.889
Not him.

41:11.170 --> 41:14.955
I'm sure I've sinned against your idol, but you're the one I've sinned against.

41:14.975 --> 41:15.796
And he owned it.

41:16.437 --> 41:28.274
And I'll get deeper into that the next time, because it's all born and down to our favorite characters.

41:29.570 --> 41:30.692
The lives underneath them.

41:32.655 --> 41:40.246
And there's a lot more to that that I need to teach them.

41:40.266 --> 41:41.949
There's a lot of lessons in that right there.

41:44.272 --> 41:46.475
People will see you mess up.

41:48.178 --> 41:48.879
They'll see it.

41:50.181 --> 41:51.743
And they'll say all kinds of evil.

41:52.645 --> 41:58.994
And always remember there's a difference in a conviction and a preference.

42:00.610 --> 42:08.300
There's a difference in what this Bible calls out and what we prefer.

42:11.443 --> 42:13.166
For instance, this is just me.

42:13.987 --> 42:17.992
I'm not judging anybody that doesn't or has them or whatever.

42:18.012 --> 42:20.134
Me, I despise tattoos.

42:20.835 --> 42:21.236
I hate them.

42:22.017 --> 42:22.778
I hate to look at them.

42:22.998 --> 42:23.699
I hate to see them.

42:24.159 --> 42:25.381
It nauseates me.

42:25.401 --> 42:26.322
I'll never get one.

42:26.690 --> 42:32.537
But I don't judge if you can paint yourself from your head to the bottom of your toes and God bless you.

42:33.358 --> 42:34.199
I'm just not doing it.

42:34.960 --> 42:37.944
That's a conviction with me.

42:38.245 --> 42:39.666
I'll die before I get more.

42:41.709 --> 42:46.555
And a preference is you like certain music?

42:47.356 --> 42:47.877
God bless you.

42:48.658 --> 42:49.399
I like this guy.

42:51.041 --> 42:55.186
If you're not convicted of it, I can't force my convictions on you.

42:57.346 --> 42:59.910
Just because I sin different than any of y'all.

43:03.215 --> 43:05.498
That's a deep point there.

43:06.480 --> 43:09.064
Don't judge me just because I sin different than you.

43:09.544 --> 43:12.068
And I won't judge you because you sin different than me.

43:12.349 --> 43:13.550
I'm not calling that sin.

43:13.610 --> 43:21.442
I'm just saying that there's a difference in convictions and what this Bible calls sin and what we prefer.

43:24.467 --> 43:26.610
You listen to Deacon Danny Kahoot.

43:26.914 --> 43:32.242
For more information, visit our website at pewfordroadbaptistchurch.com

